readme:
# Coffee Navigator

![Usage](http://cl.ly/image/1H1I472L0I2U/cn.gif)

Code navigation panel for Coffee Script, alternative to `Symbols View: Toggle File Symbols`/`CMD+R`.

# Usage

* Use command palette and search for `Coffee Navigator: Toggle`

or

* `Ctrl-Alt-N`

to toggle navigator.
